==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Genipap
<hw>Gen"i*pap</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The edible fruit of a West Indian tree (<spn>Genipa
Americana</spn>) of the order <ord>Rubiace⟦ae⟧</ord>. It is oval in
shape, as a large as a small orange, of a pale greenish color, and with
dark purple juice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Genista</ent>⟦br⟧
